fiveStar.name: Moonlit Feather
fiveStar.skill:
Increase Attack by 30.0%/30.0%/39.0%/39.0%/48.0%/48.0%/57.0%. For each Cocktail spent, randomly grant 1 of the following effects to the party:
Increase Attack by 6.0%/7.8%/7.8%/9.6%/9.6%/11.4%/11.4% (2 turns)
Increase damage by 5.0%/6.5%/6.5%/8.0%/8.0%/9.5%/9.5% (2 turns)
Increase critical rate by 4.0%/5.2%/5.2%/6.4%/6.4%/7.6%/7.6% (2 turns)
These effects do not stack. If the Cocktail spent was Tailor-Made, multiply effect by 120%. If it was Standard, multiply effect by 100%. If it was Basic, multiply effect by 50%. For every 2 Cocktails gained, reduce Yumi's cooldown time by 1 turn.

fourStar.name: Starrynight Soothsayer
fourStar.skill: Increase Attack by 12.0%/12.0%/16.0%/16.0%/20.0%/20.0%/24.0%. After using a skill, increase main target's damage by 4.8%/6.0%/6.0%/7.2%/7.2%/8.4%/8.4% for 2 turns. If this skill spends Cocktails, increase damage by 3.6%/4.5%/4.5%/5.4%/5.4%/6.3%/6.3% more.
